data.description: Take a look at this 3 bedroom, 2 bath Tri-Level with a total Update in the last 5 years. Some of the amenities included: Hardwood Hickory Floors, Solid core interior doors, remodeled upstairs bath, Updated electric and plumbing, landscaped-front and back, 6 FT cedar privacy fence, remodeled kitchen, (2012)- 95% efficient furnace w/humidifier, 50 gallon HWH, Samsung Smart Stainless Steel Refrigerator, dishwasher(Bosch), Carpeting, interior painting, Front storm door and exterior door, Lower level exterior door, A/C unit. 2013-Roof replaced/complete tear off, Siding, Soffits, over sized gutters and fascia, Cedar Fence, Added 13 inches of insulation to attic. 2014-Replaced rear sliding door. Other upgrades and amenities are: Replaced trim and interior doors, Remodeled lower level bathroom, Installed tile in lower level, installed reverse osmosis filter in kitchen, ceiling fans in bedrooms, Security system with video, shed. close to shopping and Schools, 5 minutes to I-65
data.whatILove: Very motivated seller!  This home is very low maintenance with all the updates and in a perfect location.  Perfect for a family with the cul-de-sac location.  Close to parks and low taxes since it is located in an incorporated neighborhood, but still city water and sewer.  We upgraded this home as if it was our forever home. Little details were thought of, such as automatic childproof outlets, light switches with built in light, and Kohler shower head.  The items we bought to remodel the home are quality and will last. We love our neighbors and how close it is to Schererville or Merrillville.  Great schools too.
